{"tid":602182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察通訊員自製醫生紙騙假50天　串錯頭痛英文被揭發　判囚3月","createTime":"2018-03-22T23:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T00:05:12.000Z","uid":81228,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"766af2601f71341f162a648fcfe0b30716bb5b54","tid":602182,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/164492/thumbnail/c6677a412eb1ac50aee0ffba7d20203c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F164492%2Fthumbnail%2Fc6677a412eb1ac50aee0ffba7d20203c.jpg&h=83d91371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察通訊員為偷懶，改動舊有醫生紙，在15個月內騙取了50天病假，惟他竟將頭痛英文「headache」誤打成「headace」，惹來上司懷疑並揭發。被告早前在粉嶺法院承認23項使用虛假文書罪。裁判官指他的行為違反誠信，判他入獄3個月。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1246070/xlarge/e23bcb6f79405a8bfcb9bbc00fe6f5b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1246070%2Fxlarge%2Fe23bcb6f79405a8bfcb9bbc00fe6f5b7.jpg&h=3cd12051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告麥國生在粉嶺法院承認使用虛假文書罪。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n被告麥國生，35歲，承認於2015年10月至2017年1月期間，利用40張假醫生紙，23次提出病假申請，合共取得病假50天。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>串錯頭痛英文遭揭發</strong><br />\n<br />\n被告2012年加入警隊，案發時駐守北區指揮及控制中心。案情指他於去年1月7日申請病假，並呈上由圓洲角普通科門診所發的醫生紙，上司發現當中的指他有頭痛的英文時少了一個「h」，上司感懷疑，致電醫管局查詢，發現被告未有求診，並發現被告過往已多次使用假醫生紙請假。<br />\n<br />\n被告事後承認，因不想上班，故利用圖書館的掃描器掃入舊醫生紙，再用Windows小畫家修改日期及病症，並以用作請假之用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>求情：真的患有偏頭痛</strong><br />\n<br />\n他求情時承認因愚蠢及懶惰而犯上本案，又指因他的工作崗位需要輪班，惟他工作5年仍未能適應。又因患有偏頭痛，每月都要看醫生，現已感到後悔，並願賠償3.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC229/18<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164492/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%93%A1%E8%87%AA%E8%A3%BD%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E9%A8%99%E5%81%8750%E5%A4%A9-%E4%B8%B2%E9%8C%AF%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E6%9C%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F164492%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B4%2599%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%2581%258750%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E9%258C%25AF%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2597%259B%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A3%25E6%259C%2588&d=tbxbV0lixDOzE9Xmr3OJm0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=45298644\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164492/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%93%A1%E8%87%AA%E8%A3%BD%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E9%A8%99%E5%81%8750%E5%A4%A9-%E4%B8%B2%E9%8C%AF%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E6%9C%88</a>"},{"pid":"3ca7c9a4abaa8cf69e30e4118b09196e574de397","tid":602182,"uid":133877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:46:15.000Z","msg":"偽進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab643b7ea713c227bf5fc31156f8a4981a47eea","tid":602182,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"書到用時方恨少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cfbff67c6d45739f01edb3cd9ac438c3aebea5","tid":602182,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b71d633fed89da27a7b04b48e93f7b692430430","tid":602182,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:49:15.000Z","msg":"小畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f2defed78c8556425196346a4be841ddebafbd","tid":602182,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6758543621e71afb415ebfc1fda2fdf93eaf81","tid":602182,"u